(57210, 91258, 5369, 2, 'Crying Arc', '', '2011-12-31 00:00:00', 2011, 0, 1, 7, '', 'I feel my blood\nIn vein\nThe Crying Arc\nThe Battle Drum\n \nI know you''re there\nIn dark\nBleed\nThrough your glow\n \nAnd now you''re howling\nBeheaded\nMy body\nDisarmed\n \nYou''re far\nYou''re away from here\nAnd I gather\nYour droning voice\n \nMy bloodNow in the haze\nThere you face me\nMy Crying Arc\n \nMy Blood\nNow in the haze\nThere you face me\nMy Battle Drum', 182, '', '', '', '', '', '', 0, 1, 0, '2012-12-11 22:54:06', '2015-03-12 13:57:32', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
